longBusinessSummary: Victoria Lake Inc. does not have significant operations. Previously, it was involved in the acquisition, exploration, evaluation, and development of gold properties in Tanzania. The company was formerly known as Lake Victoria Mining Company, Inc. and changed its name to Victoria Lake Inc. in March 2022. Victoria Lake Inc. was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Salt Lake City, Utah.
